data.description: Conveniently located near GA 400, local shopping centers, and accessible to the bus line. This remarkable 3-bedroom condo stands out as one of the largest units in its community.  Recently updated with meticulous attention to detail, it boasts new light fixtures, upgraded hardwood flooring on the main level and vinyl flooring upstairs, fresh coat of paint throughout. The HVAC system replaced in 2023, ensures optimal comfort year-round, complemented by a nest thermostat.  The water heater is less than 4 years old which adds to the home's efficiency. Added value comes with newer washer and dryer, as well as a stainless steel refrigerator which remains with the home.  Nestled as an end unit, privacy is paramount, enhanced by a gated back patio where lush raised garden and outdoor furniture create a serene retreat.  Recent community upgrades include a new roof replacement just a year ago and newly paved parking lot.
